{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_01","textHome":"你好。我是时雨，宫尾时雨。我以前是黑羽，@然后我喜欢育梦。还有，我喜欢机器人，自@己也会做一点点。我不是很擅长说话，所以@差不多可以了吧？和不认识的人说话很容易@累，还是请你快走吧。对不起。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":10.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102900}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_17","textHome":"机器人编程中，似乎可以使用各种各样的语言@。虽然像C语言还有Python之类的，@净是些我不明白的东西就是了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_18","textHome":"虽然刚开始接触编程，但总有一天，我想做出@个带着光学传感器的那种帅气的机器人来。@我还想在机器人竞赛上得奖。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_19","textHome":"既然弱小，就以数量取胜。这是我的最大火力@，所以绝对不会打偏。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_20","textHome":"我已经脱掉了黑羽的斗篷。之后，我会稍微变@强一点的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_21","textHome":"明明成为了魔法少女，但我甚至没有足以生存@下去的力量。即便如此，我也感觉自己克服@了一点点胆小的毛病。所以，我会更加努力@的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_22","textHome":"灯花大人说过的话语。表明魔法少女要更加优@越的那些话语。它们都一直活在我的心中。@所以，我想要告诉大家。虽然还做不到站立@于其他人之上，但如果能一起实现理想就好@了啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102900}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_00_23","textHome":"姬有着领导他人的力量。而且，她也会告诉全@世界，我们是被选中的存在。所以，我会为@了姬使用这份力量。就算是现在也毫无后悔@。这比我独自埋头于数字世界要好太多了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":102900,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102900,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102900}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102950,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1029_50_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102950,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":102950,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":